ode|7|2202}})}}\n|data-sort-value=\"Perdue, Sonny\" |[[File:Sonny Perdue headshot.jpg|100px]]<br />[[Sonny Perdue]]\n|April 25, 2017\n|-\n|data-sort-value=\"Secretary of Commerce\" |[[File:US-DeptOfCommerce-Seal.svg|75px]]<br />[[United States Secretary of Commerce|Secretary of Commerce]]<br />{{small|({{UnitedStatesCode|15|1501}})}}\n|data-sort-value=\"Ross, Wilbur\" |[[File:Wilbur Ross headshot.jpg|100px]]<br />[[Wilbur Ross]]\n|February 28, 2017\n|-\n|data-sort-value=\"Secretary of Labor\" |[[File:US-DeptOfLabor-Seal.svg|75px]]<br />[[United States Secretary of Labor|Secretary of Labor]]<br />{{small|({{UnitedStatesCode|29|551}})}}\n|data-sort-value=\"Scalia, Eugene\" |[[File:Eugene Scalia (cropped).jpg|100px]]<br />[[Eugene Scalia]]\n|September 30, 2019\n|-\n|data-sort-value=\"Secretary of Health\" |[[File:US-DeptOfHHS-Seal.svg|75px]]<br />[[United States Secretary of Health and Human Services|Secretary of Health and Human Services]]<br />{{small|(Reorganization Plan No. 1 of 1953,<br/> {{USStat|67|631}} and {{UnitedStatesCode|42|3501}})}}\n|data-sort-value=\"Azar, Alex\" |[[File:Alex Azar official portrait (cropped).jpg|100px]]<br />[[Alex Azar]]\n|January 29, 2018\n|-\n|data-sort-value=\"Secretary of Housing\" |[[File:US-DeptOfHUD-Seal.svg|75px]]<br />[[United States Secretary of Housing and Urban Development|Secretary of Housing and Urban Development]]<br />{{small|({{UnitedStatesCode|42|3532}})}}\n|data-sort-value=\"Carson, Ben\" |[[File:Ben Carson headshot.jpg|100px]]<br />[[Ben Carson]]\n|March 2, 2017\n|-\n|data-sort-value=\"Secretary of Transportation\" |[[File:US-DeptOfTransportation-Seal.svg|75px]]<br />[[United States Secretary of Transportation|Secretary of Transportation]]<br />{{small|({{UnitedStatesCode|49|102}})}}\n|data-sort-value=\"Chao, Elaine\" |[[File:Elaine Chao official portrait 2 (cropped).jpg|100px]]<br />[[Elaine Chao]]\n|January 31, 2017\n|-\n|data-sort-value=\"Secretary of Energy\" |[[File:US-DeptOfEnergy-Seal.svg|75px]]<br />[[United