xecutive Order|12608}})}}\n|data-sort-value=\"Meadows, Mark\" |[[File:Mark Meadows, Official Portrait, 113th Congress.jpg|100px|link=|alt=]]<br>[[Mark Meadows (North Carolina politician)|Mark Meadows]]\n|March 31, 2020\n|-\n|data-sort-value=\"Office of the United States Trade Representative\" |[[File:US-TradeRepresentative-Seal.svg|75px|link=|alt=]]<br>[[Office of the United States Trade Representative|Trade Representative]]<br>{{small|({{usc|19|2171}})}}\n|data-sort-value=\"Lighthizer, Robert\" |[[File:Robert E. Lighthizer official portrait (cropped).jpg|100px|link=|alt=]]<br>[[Robert Lighthizer]]\n|May 15, 2017\n|-\n|data-sort-value=\"Director of National Intelligence\"  |[[File:Seal of the Office of the Director of National Intelligence.svg|75px|link=|alt=]]<br>[[Director of National Intelligence]]<ref name=\"whitehouse.gov\">{{cite web |url=https://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2017/02/08/president-donald-j-trump-announces-his-cabinet |title=President Donald J. Trump Announces His Cabinet |date=February 8, 2017 |publisher=White House |accessdate=February 20, 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170208190158/https://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2017/02/08/president-donald-j-trump-announces-his-cabinet |archive-date=February 8, 2017 |url-status=live |df=mdy-all }}</ref><ref name=\"WashPost-coats-confirmed\">{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/powerpost/wp/2017/03/15/coats-confirmed-as-nations-new-spy-chief/ |title=Coats confirmed as nation's new spy chief |first=Karoun |last=Demirjian |date=March 15, 2017 |newspaper=[[Washington Post]] |accessdate=16 March 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170316014343/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/powerpost/wp/2017/03/15/coats-confirmed-as-nations-new-spy-chief/ |archive-date=March 16, 2017 |url-status=live |df=mdy-all }}</ref><br>{{small|({{UnitedStatesCode|50|3023}})}}\n|data-sort-value=\"Maguire, Joseph\" |[[File:Richard Grenell official photo.jpg|frameless|125x125px