NGS]]\n: Air Force Band of the Midwest, 566th Air Force Band, [[General Wayne A. Downing Peoria International Airport|Peoria ANGB]]\n*'''[[Indiana Air National Guard]]'''\n: [[122d Fighter Wing]], [[Fort Wayne Air National Guard Station|Fort Wayne ANGS]]\n: [[181st Intelligence Wing]], [[Terre Haute Air National Guard Base|Terre Haute ANGB]]\n*'''[[Iowa Air National Guard]]'''\n: [[132d Fighter Wing]], [[Des Moines Air National Guard Base|Des Moines ANGB]]\n: [[185th Air Refueling Wing]], [[Sioux City Air National Guard Base|Sioux City ANGB]]\n*'''[[Kansas Air National Guard]]'''\n: [[184th Intelligence Wing]], [[McConnell AFB]]\n: [[190th Air Refueling Wing]], [[Forbes Field|Forbes Field ANGB]] (former [[Forbes Field|Forbes AFB]]) \n*'''[[Kentucky Air National Guard]]'''\n: [[123d Airlift Wing]], Louisville ANGB/Standiford Field\n*'''[[Louisiana Air National Guard]]'''\n: [[159th Fighter Wing]], [[Naval Air Station Joint Reserve Base New Orleans|NAS JRB New Orleans]]\n*'''[[Maine Air National Guard]]'''\n: [[101st Air Refueling Wing]], [[Bangor Air National Guard Base|Bangor ANGB]] (former [[Bangor Air National Guard Base|Dow AFB]])\n*'''[[Maryland Air National Guard]]'''\n: [[175th Wing]], [[Martin State Airport]]/[[Warfield Air National Guard Base|Warfield ANGB]]\n*'''[[Massachusetts Air National Guard]]'''\n: [[102d Intelligence Wing]], [[Otis Air National Guard Base|Otis ANGB]] (former [[Otis Air National Guard Base|Otis AFB]]) \n: [[104th Fighter Wing]], Barnes ANGB\n: 253d Cyberspace Engineering Installation Group, Otis ANGB\n: Air Force Band of Northeast, 567th Air Force Band, Milford\n*'''[[Michigan Air National Guard]]'''\n: [[127th Wing]], [[Selfridge ANGB]] (former [[Selfridge ANGB|Selfridge AFB]])  \n: [[110th Attack Wing]], [[W. K. Kellogg Airport|Battle Creek ANGB]]\n: [[Alpena Combat Readiness Training Center]], Alpena\n*'''[[Minnesota Air National Guard]]'''\n: [[133d Airlift Wing]], [[Minneapolis-Saint Paul Joint Air Reserve Station|Minneapolis-St.