elavivfoundation.org/ The Tel Aviv Foundation]\n\n{{Tel Aviv District}}\n{{Largest Israeli cities}}\n{{Paralympic Summer Games Host Cities}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n<!--leave the empty space as standard-->\n\n<!--leave the empty space as standard-->\n\n[[Category:1909 establishments in the Ottoman Empire]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n[[Category:Cities in Israel]]\n[[Category:Cities in Tel Aviv District]]\n[[Category:Jewish villages in the Ottoman Empire]]\n[[Category:Mediterranean port cities and towns in Israel]]\n[[Category:Populated places established in 1909]]\n[[Category:Tel Aviv| ]]\n", "name_user": "Quebec99", "label": "safe", "comment": "fixed reference", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tel_Aviv"}
